<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>#(title)</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        .contact-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .contact-card {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0056b3;
        }
        .contact-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>DPM-PPTSP Kabupaten Nias</h1>
            <nav>
                <a href="/">Beranda</a>
                <a href="/layanan">Layanan</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="active">Kontak</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <h2>Hubungi Kami</h2>
        <p>
            Anda dapat menghubungi kami melalui kontak di bawah ini. 
            Kami siap melayani Anda pada hari Senin - Jumat ( Kecuali hari libur )
            pukul 08.00 WIB - 16.00 WIB.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <div class="contact-card">
                <h3>Alamat Kantor</h3>
                <p>
                    Jalan Arah Palmerah No. 123<br>
                    Kota Gunungsitoli<br>
                    Kabupaten Nias, Sumatera Utara 22811
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-card">
                <h3>Telepon & Fax</h3>
                <p>
                    Telepon: (0639) 123-4567<br>
                    Fax: (0639) 123-4568<br>
                    Email: dpm.pptsp@nias.go.id
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-card">
                <h3>Layanan Online</h3>
                <p>
                    Website: www.dpm-pptsp.nias.go.id<br>
                    Pengaduan: pengaduan@dpm-pptsp.nias.go.id<br>
                    Jam Layanan: 08.00 - 16.00 WIB
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-card">
                <h3>Peta Lokasi</h3>
                <p>
                    Lokasi Kantor:<br>
                    <a href="#" onclick="alert('Peta akan ditampilkan di sini')">Lihat Peta</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr style="margin: 40px 0;">

        <h3>Kirim Pesan Langsung</h3>
        <form action="/submit-pengaduan" method="POST" class="form-container">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="nama">Nama Lengkap:</label>
                <input type="text" id="nama" name="title" required placeholder="Masukkan nama Anda">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="email@anda.com">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="subject">Subjek:</label>
                <select id="subject" name="category">
                    <option value="Pengaduan">Pengaduan</option>
                    <option value="Saran">Saran</option>
                    <option value="Informasi">Informasi</option>
                    <option value="Lainnya">Lainnya</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="pesan">Pesan:</label>
                <textarea id="pesan" name="content" rows="6" required placeholder="Tuliskan pesan Anda..."></textarea>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit" class="btn">Kirim Pesan</button>
        </form>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2023 DPM-PPTSP Kabupaten Nias. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Dikembangkan oleh Tim IT DPM-PPTSP Nias</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
